{"tid":956181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美反諜機構主管警告美國人　住中資酒店或遊中國　手機電腦可被北京輕易監視","createTime":"2018-12-26T05:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T13:00:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bed6a85af12faa2859a30d658080626df8513f51","tid":956181,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:12:42.000Z","msg":"美國之聲報道，美國最高反間諜官員對中國網絡間諜能力提出新的警告，說中國政府可以輕而易舉地監視人們的智能手機和平板電腦等設備。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，美國國家反間諜與安全中心主任 William Evanina 在哥倫比亞廣播公司星期天播出的《六十分鐘》節目中說，在中國旅行、甚至在中國以外的中資酒店，人們所攜帶的智能設備都可能隨時被中國政府監視。他特別提到要注意全球中資酒店所提供的 Wi-Fi。<br />\n<br />\n他說，雖然美國的互聯網服務提供商，如 Verizon 和 AT &amp; T 是獨立的，但是在中國，互聯網是由中國政府運營的，這意味著在外國人只要連上互聯網，中國就可以立即訪問他們的信息。<br />\n<br />\nWilliam Evanina 指：「你點擊一個鏈接，也許只是一則你想要看的新聞，他們（中國）就能力進入你的硬件，他們還可以進入你的手機。」<br />\n<br />\n他說，如果他要到中國旅行，他絕對不會攜帶有著個人或公司數據的電子產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/美反諜機構主管警告美國人-住中資酒店或遊中國-手機電腦可被北京輕易監視/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%8D%E8%AB%9C%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E4%BD%8F%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%88%96%E9%81%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E5%8F%AF%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%BC%95%E6%98%93%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96%2F&d=nlZSAbnHmEPvOkfLRhKZ1P1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=96e372d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%8D%E8%AB%9C%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E4%BD%8F%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%88%96%E9%81%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E5%8F%AF%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%BC%95%E6%98%93%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96%2F&h=8ed047ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/美反諜機構主管警告美國人-住中資酒店或遊中國-手機電腦可被北京輕易監視/</a>"},{"pid":"a21261baded76132aa610c4b6c64d5a9d5c4ee68","tid":956181,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b6171eef613d50111f7bea8d0332e532d24048","tid":956181,"uid":186704,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"就算唔俾政府監視, 都好易俾Hacker入侵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df769a4580ebea3d3cc1ce4e1c2387b40afb6da","tid":956181,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53b6171eef613d50111f7bea8d0332e532d24048","tid":956181,"uid":186704,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"就算唔俾政府監視, 都好易俾Hacker入侵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4015420ec126900e992b8c44a0dad9bd40a99b0","tid":956181,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"帶部 Nokia 8210 最穩陣"}]}